0298364f2b432bd06adc5e23b6","tid":121350,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"土共組織左班打手上去搞搞震啦<br />\n本身個post讚好數量比五毛多十幾倍"},{"pid":"10fdc4a9c4f057cab617c87d3e1ffdd47f32428a","tid":121350,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7173b7cad1e6d79bc38d8d733c9cad97f2a83ae7","tid":121350,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好波喎！"},{"pid":"8284ae8cd0d31403127b81f3f38ea84b4239397f","tid":121350,"uid":21194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:58:03.000Z","msg":"致舒適品牌用戶及網友：<br />\n由於品牌在情人節社交媒體中出現失誤，引起了一些網友對於當日突發新聞的聯想和關注。這並非我們的初衷，如果造成任何不安或困擾，我們表示誠懇抱歉。<br />\n我們想向用戶承諾，舒適在香港市場超過二十年，從始至終專注產品研發、改進各項產品、努力為香港本地消費者提供更優質的剃鬚體驗。<br />\n不論在全球任何市場，我們一直都堅持創新精神，其中重要的一部分包括了重視用戶的需求、聽取和採納他們的意見。 我們堅信，只有積極接受建議，才能持續引領創新。在此，感謝你們對此事的關注和意見。<br />\n舒適(香港)"},{"pid":"3ec700857d4100a046b1d66f2114f74887463497","tid":121350,"uid":21194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"柒撚到"},{"pid":"29a5248aaf7040825322ec49a5d1814a03133fcf","tid":121350,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:01:23.000Z","msg":"警犬又要丟晒啲剃鬚刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cacec17638fa4d568c4db332684f5099410c7af","tid":121350,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:31:54.000Z","msg":"成班友對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ca61382f9e5fd5e92de31c940d4348a20b2d5b","tid":121350,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警犬又要丟晒啲剃鬚刀<img src=\"/asse